data.description: Step into your new home, this great 2 bedroom, 2-bath rambler is a gem. The kitchen is a showstopper with a large island and a built-in cooktop. The cabinets are not only functional but add a touch of style. Fresh paint brightens up the whole place, and the hardwood floors are newly sanded and sealed. The lower level welcomes you with new carpeting. The location is prime—close to shops, restaurants, schools, and more. Park your cars in the spacious 2-car garage, or large driveway, and the big backyard is perfect for outdoor fun. The lower level has an area that could be used as a 3rd bedroom. This house is ready for you to move in and make it home. Don't miss out—seize the chance to own this updated gem in a fantastic location. Quick closing available.
